Zoleka Mandela's daughter, Zanyiwe Bashala seems to be gearing up for the catwalk in future, Zoleka shared a video on Instagram of Zanyiwe doing her thing in the mall. Twirls and all. Dressed in a pink Cinderella dress, that was accessorized with sunglasses and a tiara, the little girl oozed confidence. Zanyiwe smiled and waved as she modeled in the mall. Watch out world - this lil girl could be SA's next supermodel or entertainer!